Optional Dependencies
=====================

Kivy has a number of optional (runtime) dependencies:

 * Pygame
 * Gst-Python
 * Enchant
 * OpenCV
 * PIL
 * PyCairo
 * PyEnchant
 * PyGST

For more information, see here:
http://kivy.org/docs/installation/installation.html

